<div class="brand">Fishing Tournament System</div>
<div class="address-bar">Charleston, SC</div>

<%= render 'layouts/navigation' %>

<div class="container">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>
                <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Angler
                    <strong><%= link_to 'Sign in', page_path('signin'), class: "btn btn-default" %> or <%= link_to 'Register', page_path('register'), class: "btn btn-default" %></strong>
                </h2>
                <hr>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-responsive img-border-left" src="/assets/fish4.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>The Fishing Tournament System provides prospective anglers with a central location to obtain information on available fishing tournaments in their area as well as offer functionality for those anglers to register (including paying registration fees) and participate in tournaments.  Registered anglers can:</p>
                <li>Sign up for a fishing tournament</li>
                <li>Pay the necessary fees for a tournament</li>
                <li>Obtain information about fishing clubs in the area</li>
                <li>View and tag photos and details about past, present and future tournaments</li>
                <li>Connect and share on social media</li>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
